  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6542 sitting right in the heart of massive negative gamma concentration (-17B at 6540), dealers are forced to buy this breakout momentum as they're short gamma in a BREAKOUT regime. The wall_break event confirms dealers just got steamrolled through multiple negative GEX levels (6530-6540 cluster), creating amplified buying pressure that should continue until we hit the positive gamma ceiling at 6580 where dealers will start selling into strength. Watch 6580 as the critical resistance where dealer flow reverses from buying to selling, while any dip back toward the 6525-6540 cluster will trigger more mechanical dealer buying.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect continued upside momentum until 6580 where dealers will start pushing back.",
